## To Complete Integration

1. Open Xcode
2. Right-click on Views folder > Add Files to "Gadfly"
3. Add: MorningPrepView.swift, QuickCheckView.swift
4. Right-click on Services folder > Add Files to "Gadfly"
5. Add: MorningPrepService.swift, QuickCheckService.swift, SmartLocationService.swift
6. In ContentView.swift, change CheckoutChecklistView to QuickCheckView
7. Build and run

