## ADHD Design Principles Applied

1. Make the right thing the easy thing (3 taps max)
2. Zero setup required (smart home detection)
3. No decision fatigue (only essential items by default)
4. Multi-sensory feedback (voice + haptics + visual)
5. Quick escape hatch ("Not leaving" button)
6. Progressive disclosure (+ More items for power users)
